Class RowStatisticsImpl

java.lang.Object
org.apache.hadoop.hbase.coprocessor.example.row.stats.RowStatisticsImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
RowStatistics
@Private public class RowStatisticsImpl extends Object implements RowStatistics
Holder for accumulating row statistics in RowStatisticsCompactionObserver Creates various cell, row, and total stats.

    • shipped

      public void shipped(RawCellBuilder cellBuilder)
      Clone the cell refs so they can be cleaned up by Shipper.shipped(). Doing this lazily here, rather than eagerly in the above two methods can save us on some allocations. We might change the largestCell/largestRow multiple times between shipped() calls.
